title: The History of Marijuana Narrated by Woody Harrelson
description:
The History of Marijuana Narrated by Woody Harrelson

This is an excellent walk through the history of Marijuana. Woody Harrelson, well know Marijuana reform advocate, narrates this 1 hour and 19 minute documentary.

The film shows the complete history of Marijuana prohibition and how the various laws and institutions associated with it&#039;s prohibition came to be. The documentary is factually based and has little commentary either for or against Marijuana while the film is clearly against prohibition.
